{"id":"209239","title":"虐婚99天：总裁的天价新娘","writer":"柒月绯然","dateline":"1532185581","updatetime":"1532185581","isover":"1","filesize":"1334047","linecount":"16705","wordcount":"649699","imgpath":"https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-FvqNzGV/0/5946a681/Th/i-FvqNzGV-Th.jpg","hash":"zongcaidetianjiaxinniang","urlhash":"jjxsw_29098","sign":"","desc":"文案：\r\n因为巨额的彩礼，她把自己“卖”给了景子墨\r\n本以为，景子墨能够成为她一生的倚靠和挚爱\r\n可新婚之夜，他扔下她离开，从此以后再也没有踏进过她的房间。\r\n“这是你得到景太太的代价！”他经常带着不同的女人出现在他们家里，她是景太太，过的却还不如一个女佣。\r\n“我们离婚，我什么都不要，给你自由也让我自由。”相互折磨，没有爱情的婚姻让夏浅感觉很疲惫，也累了。\r\n事到如今，景子墨忽然发现，原来夏浅才该是和他白头到老的那个人。\r\n只是那颗心，早已被伤害和绝望，连呼吸都变的那般的疼痛。","hot":"0","num":"0","cid":"275","suggcate":"总裁豪门,总裁,腹黑,霸道,豪门,宠文","suggcids":"275","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"0","clicknum":"0","isvip":"0","ish":"0","age":"现代","channel":"女","isqiniu":"0","list":"0,21z,4g3,6pz,91s,b43,d8o,f89,hix,jqv,m4y,o52,qb5,sll,ucr,wnp,ynn,1106,134c,1561,177d,1913,1b3e,1dc1,1ffn,1hdt,1jdn,1lb3,1nfq,1pk3,1rn0,1tl8,1vsu,1y0v,20bv,22nu,24g1,26nq,28u2,2avf,2d2s,2f37,2hg6,2jsj,2m68,2os6,2r5w,2t39,2v68,2xb8,2zby,31t0,341p,366o,38gs,3ar1,3cvy,3ez1,3gzf,3j7w,3lbh,3nd3,3pes,3rbg,3t63,3v5b,3wxd,3yv0,40pq,42ui,453a,46xk,48m2,4ayh,4cyg,4f12,4h5t,4ip2,4kb1,4m3r,4ntz,4pkl,4rio,4t5t,4uxn,4wzk,4yve,50u5,535o,551h,56wl,58sw,5anp,5cit,5e7g,5g80,5ijp,5k54,5m8e,5oax,5q6s,5s44,5tw1,5vx3,5y0h,5zyh,622s,63xa,65gd,67es,694o,6b0c,6cpg,6epg,6gd3,6ido,6kft,6m8u,6ohi,6qme,6sln,6umu,6wj4,6y53,6zqm,71w5,73p6,75zb,77yc,7a3m,7cam,7e2i,7gd7,7ikj,7kkj,7mbq,7ohu,7qo6,7sx8,7vkv,7xqe,803m,82hm,84n9,86m3,88r9,8axy,8cph,8eqh,8gme,8iot,8kvm,8ng8,8pr0,8rx7,8u06,8wb5,8yea,90pn,92vr,9574,97n4,99yz,9ci4,9f5t,9hrl,9kf3,9mjz,9oo3,9qwp,9t38,9vlf,9xzm,a0au,a2tf,a54m,a7du,a9hi,abrh,ae5m,agh5,aiyf,alc0,antp,aqau,asx0,avk6,ay6b,b0x0,b33v,b600,b82r,ba8w,bciy,bezr,bhvg,bk95,bmub,bp8h,brpt,bu7a,bwno,bz3s,c1bw,c3n6,c61z,c893,cakj,cdcr,cfm7,chs0,ck7x,cmpj,cp9b,crv2,cud5,cwop,cz8n,d1bh,d3u7,d6c1,d8wb,db7h,ddvh,dg8g,dif7,dknv,dmw2,dpjs,drwe,du6f,dwg8,dyd2,e11k,e3uh,e65s,e899,eaft,ecpq,eewm,eh5i,ejpb,e